# Required. 32-byte random secret used to encrypt the credentials cookie that
# drives transparent re-login when the upstream SWMaestro session dies. Must be
# a base64-encoded 32-byte value. Generate with:
#
#   openssl rand -base64 32
#
# If this secret rotates, existing sessions lose their auto-relogin ability
# and users fall back to the normal /login flow on the next session expiry.
OPENSOMA_CREDENTIAL_SECRET=
